description:
The middle sister. This 23 years old graduate from high school works as a clerk in an apparel shop, she is an expert on calligraphy and shogi, and despite her rough personality, she has the best communication skills of the three and also the most experienced on romantic affairs, to the point she is the expert the other sisters go to see when they need good advice on how to find love.
Source: http://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Watanuki-san_Chi_No
name: Watanuki Futaba
